author: COMSOL
description: This is an example of a redox flow battery that simulates charge and discharge during a load cycle. A two-dimensional model that includes mass, charge, and momentum transport is used for the electrochemical cell. A zero-dimensional tank model simulates the reactant concentrations in the electrolyte outside the cell.
